wn invaders from another part. All while we have the house, senate, and presidency. We won a critical election to get our representatives in positions of power and our representatives are flooding your neighborhood with unassimilated arabs.</p>\n<p>In my home town over the past 1.5 years I have noticed a severe surge in Indians and arabs. They are taking over city council, they are in every store, every school, and next to me in traffic. Today, 20 feet from my house I saw a fully hijabed Islamist woman, covered top to bottom, and a man who looked like he weighed 130lbs walking. They looked fresh off the boat walking in my middle class neighborhood.</p>\n<p>Tell me what good is voting and winning an election when our own representatives betray us?</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 22, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsL6Sy3d", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 259, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8604721, "raw_content": "", "author": "TateDemarcus", "created": 1778167774868, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Salutations", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "cdn.5mind.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsL6Sy3d.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://cdn.5mind.com/uploads/production/OeTlFH5ZIoiqDBEC4Sc2a/image/GFAFN7utLU0HD8xaGBtDH.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/eCvWlsXmPrfnt0ZS.jpeg", "width": 512, "content-type": "jpeg", "height": 640}], "blurhash": "UEC?+Yo~0,s9yGbcKRr